title: DDFP 339: Free agency fantasy impact & new rules
itunes:title: DDFP 339: Free agency fantasy impact & new rules
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to review the latest new rule proposals in the NFL as well as suggest a few of their own. NFL Fantasy guru Michael Fabiano then joins the show to discuss how free agency has changed the landscape in fantasy football. Plus, the search for the greatest movie producer Black Tie has never seen begins on #DDFP Bracketology. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
